THESSALONIA B. PRINCE v. COMMISSIONER OF CORRECTION (14738)

Heiman, Spear and Hennessy, Js.

Argued January 11 decision released February 13, 1996 *923Ronald A. Stone, special public defender, for the appellant (petitioner). Robert J. Scheinblum, deputy assistant state’s attorney, with whom, on the brief, were Michael Dearington, state’s attorney, and John Dropick, assistant state’s attorney, for the appellee (respondent). PER CURIAM.

The judgment is affirmed.
